---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
	title="About Dean Tool"
	description="Learn the story behind Dean Tool's dark lounge sound and stage persona."
	active="about"
>
	<section class="section">
		<div class="story-grid">
			<article class="bio-card">
				<span class="eyebrow">The Story</span>
				<h1 class="display-title">A voice built for velvet rooms and dangerous timing.</h1>
				<p class="muted">
					Dean Tool came up through dim jazz basements, after-hours radio sets, and stages where the
					crowd wanted elegance with a little trouble in it. The sound still carries that tension:
					classic phrasing, modern edge, and arrangements that never stay polite for long.
				</p>
				<p class="muted">
					Across decades of records, Dean has moved from smoky standards into bolder, stranger material
					without losing the core identity. The suit got sharper. The rooms got darker. The songs got
					better.
				</p>
			</article>
			<aside class="quote-card">
				<span class="eyebrow">Artist Statement</span>
				<blockquote>"Make it elegant first. Make it unforgettable second. Make it dangerous third."</blockquote>
				<p>
					That balance shapes the whole project: romance, swagger, and just enough shadow to keep the
					audience leaning in.
				</p>
			</aside>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="section-panel">
			<div class="section-heading">
				<div>
					<span class="eyebrow">What Defines The Sound</span>
					<h2 class="section-title">Classic craft with a modern silhouette.</h2>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="stats-grid">
				<div class="stat-card">
					<strong>Jazz</strong>
					<span>Roomy arrangements, brass warmth, and a slow-burn pulse.</span>
				</div>
				<div class="stat-card">
					<strong>Soul</strong>
					<span>Melodic phrasing that lands heavy without needing to shout.</span>
				</div>
				<div class="stat-card">
					<strong>Noir</strong>
					<span>Visuals and moods pulled from midnight streets and stage light.</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</SiteLayout>
